episodes.title: Of Cults and Kardashians
episodes.description: Kate and Leisha have both been hitting the cult documentaries pretty hard and are back from break ready to talk about, 'Love Has Won: The Cult of Mother God' and some others. If you haven't watched it consider this your spoiler warning.  PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey is produced and edited by Arwen Nicks, and mixed by Valentino Rivera. Follow us on Instagram @ThePantsPod or send us an email at kateandleisha@gmail.com. Our music is by Carol Parra @csssuxxx and our artwork is by Lovefoxxx. Learn more about your ad choices.
